<!--
  Piston, Harmony — Inversion Examples
  Transcribed from:
    Ex. 150 (p.89)  — Ch.9: First inversions in C major: V6 I I6 IV I I6 II6 V
    Ex. 155 (p.91)  — Ch.9: Extended I6 progressions in C major
    Ex. 222 (p.118) — Ch.11: Cadential 6/4 in four harmonic contexts

  Ground truth Roman numerals from Piston's text used as validation reference.
  These are textbook examples — labels are unambiguous ground truth.
-->
<score-partwise version="3.1">
